<p>Friday 7 December</p>
<p>Dull &amp; cold.<br/>Early morning (6 a.m.) trip with Casualty wire<br/>Run to Adv. Dressing Station at Khandahah Farm<br/>Nothing else to do today<br/>Heard the sad news of Reg Cannon's death.  His head was blown right off last night.<br/>Had a look over the RE8 aeroplane which landed on rough ground near our camp &amp; was considerably smashed.<br/>The bow hut in which I am living is very comfortable.  We have a fire going all day long.</p>
